{"tid":1876002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10名在湖北的港人確診感染新型冠狀病毒","createTime":"2020-02-12T06:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T08:07:09.000Z","uid":28114,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d68b8ab9ac99550b10a6629d053ace04abbe0bd1","tid":1876002,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1508108_1_20200212141446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1508108_1_20200212141446.jpg&h=ffcaa72b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10名在湖北的香港人確診感染新型冠狀病毒。（shutterstock）<br />\n<br />\n政府證實，10名港人在湖北確診感染新型冠狀病毒，涉及3個家庭，其中7人在武漢，3人在恩施。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局發言人表示，特區政府近日收到內地相關單位通報，以及駐武漢經貿辦事處的通知，得悉有關情況後，已立即要求駐武漢辦事處為這批人士提供一切可行協助，其中6人已在短時間內入住當地醫院，其餘4人則自行到醫院就診，所有人情況大致穩定。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又說，駐武漢辦事處會一直與他們保持緊密聯繫提供協助，確保他們得到適當的治療和照顧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508108-20200212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508108-20200212.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=d6632b5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508108-20200212.htm&h=e14f7cc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508108-20200212.htm</a>"},{"pid":"20dba785c70029a0759e17a2351dd26527d5b441","tid":1876002,"uid":92299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"一家人最緊要齊齊整整.jpg"},{"pid":"037cf63634676bf92b20773c5eb7fcf9d73a7dcb","tid":1876002,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"可防可控"},{"pid":"f779b2413c164c48626ef1954a3157330b88fe8b","tid":1876002,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"上咗去就唔好返嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s